# Count even numbers
command 'from test.even_numbers take 10'
---
> +-------+---------+
> |  id   |  value  |
> +-------+---------+
> |  120  |   120   |
> |  118  |   118   |
> |  116  |   116   |
> |  114  |   114   |
> |  112  |   112   |
> |  110  |   110   |
> |  108  |   108   |
> |  106  |   106   |
> |  104  |   104   |
> |  102  |   102   |
> +-------+---------+
> 

# Verify filter worked correctly - should have 60 even numbers (2,4,6...120)
command 'from test.even_numbers aggregate { count: count(value) }'
---
> +---------+
> |  count  |
> +---------+
> |   60    |
> +---------+
> 
